platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Terry Cavanaghs Super Hexagon is quite simply one of the most challenging games weve ever played. A pulsating chiptunes soundtrack underscores the danger as swirling walls close in around you and you race to escape the contracting maze. With the geometric action heaping on the punishment (the easiest difficulty is appropriately labeled Hard), every small achievement feels like a massive victory, whether youre topping your high score or overcoming a singularly tricky section.

Terry Cavanaghs Super Hexagon is quite simply one of the most challenging games weve ever played. A pulsating chiptunes soundtrack underscores the danger as swirling walls close in around you and you race to escape the contracting maze. With the geometric action heaping on the punishment (the easiest difficulty is appropriately labelled Hard), every small achievement feels like a massive victory, whether youre topping your high score or overcoming a singularly tricky section.

Conu par Terry Cavanagh, Super Hexagon est sans aucun doute lun des jeux les plus ardus auxquels nous ayons jamais jou. La bande son 8-bit palpitante ponctue le danger omniprsent, alors que les murs tournoyants dun labyrinthe nous encerclent et nous pressent den trouver lissue. Entre gomtrie oppressante et difficult impitoyable, chaque moment de succs procure la sensation dune immense victoire, que vous amlioriez votre record ou que vous sortiez indemne dune situation prilleuse.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: This is still one of our favorites. Few games are this satisfying to master.
